PRIOR: Confident C - [0.1 0.1 0.8]
------------------------------------------------------------
Obs  Surprise    VFE     Complexity  Accuracy   Posterior
0       2.637    1.966      0.878    -1.088   [0.64285714 0.07142857 0.28571429]
