1. Setting up Simple Agent Model:
----------------------------------------
  Modalities: 2 (location_sensor, reward_sensor)
  State factors: 2 (location, reward_available)
  Observations: location ∈ {0,1,2}, reward ∈ {0,1}
  States: location ∈ {0,1,2}, reward_available ∈ {0,1}

